{
  "stem": "23428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you see, since, I think, the teachers didn't make a big fuss about this, nobody else much did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were not harassed in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was a big school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was probably, oh, maybe 500, 600 kids, exactly of the same type that my kids go to now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a good school and rather rigorous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of Hungarians sent their kids there, because it was for them a way to give their children a more cosmopolitan education.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were very serious about teaching Western culture, and of course, particularly German literature and history and culture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March, 1944, it was all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In March, 1944, suddenly the streets of Budapest were filled with German soldiers and SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a rabidly fascist government came to power.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, stepwise.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First a less rabid one, under Imredy, and then a really bad one, very soon after.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's when peace ended.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, we had to have our high school-- the-- the-- the Hungarian children of Jewish background and us were given a I think two- or three-week early high school graduation exam, just because the school didn't feel they could hold us any longer, so we made a baccalaureate examination that was a few weeks ahead of the rest of the class.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was your status at the time, as a Jew or as a German?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, as far as the Hungarians concerned, of course we were-- we were both of these, both Jews and Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So, you know, very soon I think the yellow star policy-- I mean, the legislation arrived in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I mentioned before, we never-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we never obeyed that law.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
